description: Give your frame the protection it deserves. These grippy honeycomb panels are easy to apply and super durable.Durable 380 micron PVC protects your frame from scoring, with gripped texture.Semi-rigid, non-yellowing and UV-resistant.1 large piece for the downtube.5 chevrons for the chainstay, down tube or top tube.3 circles for cable wear.Fits most XC, marathon and trail frames.
name: ALL MOUNTAIN STYLE Honeycomb Frame Guard
